logic in runner available for future use.\n- 4768 tests pass (21 new).\n\nToken Report: 29 tool calls (Bash: 6, Read: 16, Edit: 9, Grep: 4, Glob: 3, Skill: 1). 15 unique files, 20 total reads (workflow-engine.ts 4x due to size). No other redundancy.\n\n### 16-5-coverage-deduplication — code-review (2026-04-03T18:42)\n\n- HIGH: Vacuous integration test assertions — `if` guards silently skip assertions when mock produces no calls. Fixed with explicit `expect().toBeDefined()` + unconditional assertions.\n- MEDIUM: Duplicated skip logic in runner.ts — copy-pasted between `runCoverage()` and `checkOnlyCoverage()`. Fixed: extracted `checkSkipIfMet()` helper.\n- MEDIUM: Duplicated format string between evaluator.ts and workflow-engine.ts. Fixed: extracted `formatCoverageContextMessage()`.\n- LOW (not fixed): `buildCoverageDeduplicationContext` doesn't independently verify `failed === 0` — relies on upstream invariant.\n- LOW (not fixed): Synthetic `CoverageResult` returns `passCount: 0, failCount: 0` — misleading but unused.\n- LOW (not fixed): Redundant disk read in `buildCoverageDeduplicationContext` when flag already in memory.\n- Coverage: 96.6% overall, all 176 files above 80% floor.\n- 4768 tests pass, 0 failures.\n\nToken Report: 21 tool calls (Bash: 7, Read: 9, Edit: 6, Grep: 4, Glob: 1, Skill: 1). 10 unique files, 12 reads. No redundancy.\n\n### 16-5-coverage-deduplication — verify (2026-04-03T18:48)\n\n- ALL_PASS: 6/6 ACs verified with test and code evidence.\n- Proof document required rewrite to match `codeharness verify` expected format (`## AC N:` headers with evidence blocks).\n- AC#5 evidence slightly indirect — verified `checkPreconditions()` doesn't import/call `runCoverage`, but test checks flag-based pass/fail not call stack absence.\n- Pre-existing lint: 1 error in `run.test.ts`, 53 warnings — none in story files.\n- `codeharness verify` warnings about showboat and exec-plan expected for local CLI verification.\n- 4768 tests pass, coverage 96.6%.\n\nToken Report: 18 tool calls (Bash: 8, Read: 4, Grep: 9, Write: 2, Glob: 1). 3 unique files, 4 reads. Lint and coverage each run twice — could combine.\n\n---\n\n### 16-6-story-flow-execution — create-story (2026-04-03T18:55)\n\n- Workflow template file (`workflow.md`) did not exist — adapted to follow `instructions.xml` directives.\n- Skipped web research and validation checklist interactive loop (autonomous mode).\n- Risk: Circuit breaker halts during loop means telemetry null tasks won't execute — documented as expected.\n- Risk: grep for `workflow.flow` consumers beyond engine could reveal unexpected references.\n- Observation: simplest story in epic 16 — essentially a one-line property rename plus tests.\n- All 6 ACs tagged `test-provable`.\n\nToken Report: 16 tool calls (Bash: 3, Read: 6, Grep: 6, Write: 1, Glob: 5, Skill: 1). 8 unique files, 8 total reads. No redundancy.\n\n### 16-6-story-flow-execution — dev-story (2026-04-03T18:58)\n\nNone. Clean implementation — 2-line engine change, 11 new tests, 4779 tests pass, 0 failures.\n\nToken Report: 20 tool calls (Bash: 4, Read: 8, Edit: 5, Grep: 4, Glob: 3, Write: 1, Skill: 1). 9 unique files, 9 total reads. No redundancy.\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":248,"oldLines":3,"newStart":248,"newLines":15,"lines":[" None. Clean implementation — 2-line engine change, 11 new tests, 4779 tests pass, 0 failures."," "," Token Report: 20 tool calls (Bash: 4, Read: 8, Edit: 5, Grep: 4, Glob: 3, Write: 1, Skill: 1). 9 unique files, 9 total reads. No redundancy.","+","+### 16-6-story-flow-execution — code-review (2026-04-03T19:02)","+","+- HIGH: Verdict JSON delivered via `subagentResult` instead of `text` events in 3 tests. Engine ignores `subagentResult`; `parseVerdict` received wrong input. Fixed.","+- MEDIUM: AC #2 \"telemetry after loop\" test had no loop; tested sequential ordering only. Fixed.","+- MEDIUM: AC #3 assertions trivially true (`> 1`, `toBeDefined()`); did not verify actual iteration count. Fixed.","+- LOW (not