{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HaKsGfwUEL1XZuBs1vJB7R","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Harness Cost Report\n2\t\n3\tTotal API-equivalent cost: $314.58\n4\tTotal API calls: 2406\n5\tAverage cost per story: $3.38 (79 stories)\n6\t\n7\t## Cost by Token Type\n8\t\n9\t| Type | Tokens | Rate | Cost | % |\n10\t|------|--------|------|------|---|\n11\t| Cache reads | 129,557,447 | $1.50/MTok | $194.34 | 62% |\n12\t| Cache writes | 3,688,962 | $18.75/MTok | $69.17 | 22% |\n13\t| Output | 679,748 | $75/MTok | $50.98 | 16% |\n14\t| Input | 6,542 | $15/MTok | $0.10 | 0% |\n15\t\n16\t## Cost by Phase\n17\t\n18\t| Phase | Calls | Cost | % |\n19\t|-------|-------|------|---|\n20\t| verify | 1156 | $140.23 | 44.6% |\n21\t| orchestrator | 257 | $55.88 | 17.8% |\n22\t| create-story | 301 | $34.46 | 11.0% |\n23\t| dev-story | 294 | $33.03 | 10.5% |\n24\t| code-review | 244 | $29.15 | 9.3% |\n25\t| retro | 154 | $21.82 | 6.9% |\n26\t\n27\t## Cost by Tool\n28\t\n29\t| Tool | Calls | Cost | % |\n30\t|------|-------|------|---|\n31\t| Bash | 794 | $89.24 | 28.4% |\n32\t| Read | 522 | $72.76 | 23.1% |\n33\t| Edit | 458 | $56.77 | 18.0% |\n34\t| Agent | 306 | $44.84 | 14.3% |\n35\t| Skill | 54 | $19.67 | 6.3% |\n36\t| Grep | 149 | $16.18 | 5.1% |\n37\t| Write | 44 | $6.33 | 2.0% |\n38\t| Glob | 49 | $5.12 | 1.6% |\n39\t| TodoWrite | 26 | $3.35 | 1.1% |\n40\t| ToolSearch | 4 | $0.33 | 0.1% |\n41\t\n42\t## Top 10 Most Expensive Stories\n43\t\n44\t| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n45\t|-------|-------|------|---|\n46\t| unknown | 183 | $47.90 | 15.2% |\n47\t| 5-1-flow-execution-sequential-steps | 65 | $8.84 | 2.8% |\n48\t| 2-1-workflow-yaml-json-schema | 69 | $8.51 | 2.7% |\n49\t| 16-6-story-flow-execution | 52 | $7.00 | 2.2% |\n50\t| 9-2-custom-workflow-creation | 64 | $6.83 | 2.2% |\n51\t| 3-2-embedded-agent-templates | 49 | $6.42 | 2.0% |\n52\t| 14-3-activity-display-driver-integration | 48 | $6.35 | 2.0% |\n53\t| 16-3-telemetry-writer | 46 | $6.