{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CXW19n8rHLxWYt31uFtQEm","type":"tool_result","content":"6020\t\n6021\t---\n6022\t\n6023\t## Session Scorecard\n6024\t\n6025\t| Metric | Value |\n6026\t|--------|-------|\n6027\t| Stories completed | 1 (16-5) |\n6028\t| Total ACs verified | 6/6 (100%) |\n6029\t| HIGH bugs caught by review | 1 |\n6030\t| MEDIUM bugs caught by review | 2 |\n6031\t| Tests added | 21 (4747 -> 4768) |\n6032\t| Coverage | 96.6% |\n6033\t| Session cost | ~$4.80 |\n6034\t| Cost per story | $4.80 |\n6035\t| Retries | 0 |\n6036\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Tz8YkXPmsrCgh2PY4nUQKs","session_id":"e648a229-0e5b-4ea4-9861-593afdfcccd5","uuid":"b135e1f8-a2d0-4d8e-97d2-315b09b7a3fc","timestamp":"2026-04-03T19:17:42.169Z"}
